               stealing a silk handkerchief, value 1 s.
            </rs> the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t17791208-21-victim237" type="victimName">
                     Richard
                      Bolton
                  <interp inst="t17791208-21-victim237" type="surname" value="Bolton"></interp>
